description: [``botocore``] This release adds support to describe the synchronization status of the account-level block public access feature for your Amazon Lightsail buckets.
[``botocore``] Removes Amazon RDS on VMware with the deletion of APIs related to Custom Availability Zones and Media installation
[``botocore``] This release adds subfields, ErrorMessage, Retryable, to the AthenaError response object in the GetQueryExecution API when a query fails.
